---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-surface-900 mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-surface-400 mb-8">Last updated: July 2025</p>

    <div class="prose prose-surface max-w-none text-surface-600 space-y-4">
      <p>These Terms of Service govern your use of {Astro.locals.hostname} (the "Site"), operated by Competitive LLC. By accessing or using the Site, you agree to be bound by these terms.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mt-8 mb-3">Use of the Site</h2>
      <p>You agree to use the Site only for lawful purposes and in accordance with these Terms. You may not use the Site to engage in any activity that disrupts, interferes with, or damages the Site or its underlying infrastructure.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mt-8 mb-3">Content Accuracy</h2>
      <p>We strive to provide accurate and up-to-date product information and pricing. However, product specifications, prices, and availability are subject to change without notice. We do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of any information on the Site.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mt-8 mb-3">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>This Site participates in affiliate marketing programs, including the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program. When you click on an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. This does not influence our product rankings or recommendations, which are based on objective criteria.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mt-8 mb-3">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content on the Site — including text, graphics, logos, data compilations, and software — is the property of Competitive LLC or its content providers and is protected by applicable copyright and intellectual property laws.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mt-8 mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>Competitive LLC shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of or inability to use the Site or from any purchase made through affiliate links on the Site.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mt-8 mb-3">Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. Continued use of the Site after changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-surface-900 mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about these Terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@externalssds.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">support@externalssds.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
